  {
    "hotel_id": "6587786",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/masil-guesthouse-jeju/hotel/jeju-island-kr.html",
    "name": "Masil Guesthouse Jeju",
    "detail": "There is no elevator at this hostel. If you have a lot of luggages, you may get very tired by the time you get to your room. The lights in the hallway are dimmed but the place is safe. The bathroom is inside the room as standard Korean bathroom. I booked a single room but got upgraded to a three person room. The room is well soundproof. If you open the window, you can hear the airplanes. It's right beside the Jeju intercity bus terminal, which will take you to anywhere around the island. Free laundry but it will cost 3000 won to dry your clothes. If you are not in a rush, you can hang dry your clothes in the room. They provide clothe dryer rack in the room. Convenient stores and cheap restaurants are around if you're adventurous. Downtow is 20 minutes walk away. I highly recommend this hostel if you stay in the Jeju-si area. ",
