    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/seastay-hotel-spa/hotel/jeju-island-kr.html",
    "name": "Seastay hotel & Spa",
    "detail": "A spacious, modern house with a great sea view! Make dream with ocean! The host is really helpful and friendly. We keep exchanging info during our stay and provided good recommendations for food and amenities in the area The room is quite neat and clean~feel so comfortable~ It is located at a place with cute little coffee shops, restaurants nearby. Of course, it has an amazing ocean view - you can also go out fishing just infront of the door. Also I was worried whether the house will be cold since we traveled in Jaunary but the heating system was really good. It's a very enjoyable stay at this place. Not much I can stay about this place cause we arrived quite late. But few thing I can say about this stay is that the host is a very kind and helpful person, it's a peaceful neighborhood. Overall, very good and pleasant experience. My boyfriend and I will definitely consider this as no. 1 option next time we travel to Jeju, and the place really made my experience at Jeju Island memorable. ",
